|---------------------------------|----------------|------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="1cfca-108">ErrorWrapper [] pArr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cfca-108">ErrorWrapper[] pArr</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="1cfca-109">Errorwrapper の ErrorWrapper [10] (77)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cfca-109">ErrorWrapper[10] of ErrorWrapper(77)</span></span>|`Int[10]`|  
|<span data-ttu-id="1cfca-110">オブジェクト [] pArr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cfca-110">Object[] pArr</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="1cfca-111">Errorwrapper の ErrorWrapper [10] (77)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cfca-111">ErrorWrapper[10] of ErrorWrapper(77)</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="1cfca-112">`VARIANT[10]` の `VT_ERROR`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cfca-112">`VARIANT[10]` of `VT_ERROR`</span></span>|  
